{"tid":1934022,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位大力share呢段NYT講中共網絡戰既片!!!!!","createTime":"2020-03-19T16:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T10:06:33.000Z","uid":179167,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2daf0543d58808ab93a3c2668a198519ef261ebe","tid":1934022,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LwqhvRcBrK4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLwqhvRcBrK4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=dcae132c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LwqhvRcBrK4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都知中國而家發動緊輿論戰spin走所有責任<br />\n但係連登reddit/twitter網軍講幾多都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔及大外媒講咁有威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢段片係New York Times 整, 係外國公信力大好多<br />\n清晰易明地講解中共所有假新聞同埋制度形象技倆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位twitter師留言不妨留呢條youtube link, <br />\n再加句: if you still think China is somehow reliable in this containment of the outbreak, try watch this NYT videos.<br />\n或者: this video may give you a brief explanation of how Chinese propaganda machine works, and why they have unreasonably many foreign reporter in USA, to either be a spy, collecting data, or lobbying, or simply organize attack to any protest supporting HK or Uighurs.<br />\n<br />\n大力推, 入到去就like, 係自己facebook朋友圈子間share, 推爆個view數佢, 推佢上熱門. 上twitter又可以用呢條片, 有人整左咁好既素材, 冇理由唔用下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好俾支那走甩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327b518421f09fdc882833c08531f7cb224df340